
## Step 2: Remove All .DS_Store Files
After listing all .DS_Store files, you can remove them by running:
```
find . -name '.DS_Store' -type f -delete
```

## Step 3: Commit the Changes
Once all .DS_Store files have been removed, commit these changes to the repository with the following command:
```
git add .
git commit -m "Remove .DS_Store files and update .gitignore"
